metadata.name: Whitebouquet
metadata.description:
There, against the background of white snow, the Master passes to the edge of the worlds. 
It's time to hit the road. And the boat is already waiting for him. 
Don't be afraid to ask a question - he opened the portal, maybe you'll get an answer soon. 
The wild worlds of Vava is here
Turn on the sound
